# template-version: 2026-07.22
# Line-ending policy: the repo is LF everywhere. Formatters that check the
# WORKING TREE (Prettier's endOfLine default is "lf") fail repo-wide when
# core.autocrlf=true (the Git-for-Windows default) re-materializes tracked
# LF files as CRLF on a fresh checkout or branch switch — a red check gate
# disguised as a formatting problem. This file pins the policy in-repo.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary formats Git must never rewrite:
*.ico binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf binary
